OURCE NOTEBOOK ON STAFF DEVELOPMENT.     FOCUSES ON LIBRARY STAFF DEVELOPMENT. THE INTRODUCTION PROVIDES BACKGROUND ANDA BRIEF CONCEPTUAL OVERVIEW OF STAFF DEVELOPMENT. THE FIRST SECTION OFDOCUMENTS PROVIDES EXAMPLES OF DATA GATHERING TOOLS AND APPROACHES TOGATHERING INFORMATION. THE SECOND GROUP OF DOCUMENTS ILLUSTRATES METHODS OFDESCRIBING AND ANALYZING CURRENT STAFF DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMMES, AND THE FINALSECTION CONTAINS EXAMPLES OF RECOMMENDATIONS FOR NEW APPROACHES TO STAFFDEVELOPMENT WHICH HAVE BEEN MADE BY LIBRARIES